trans-unit.source: Represents a specific type of access rule that is used to allow or deny an Active Directory object an extended right.
trans-unit.target: Representerer en bestemt type tilgangsregel som brukes til å gi eller avslå en Active Directory-objekt en utvidet høyre.

trans-unit.source: Extended rights are special operations that are not covered by the standard set of access rights.
trans-unit.target: Utvidet rettigheter som er spesielle operasjoner som ikke dekkes av settet med tilgangsrettigheter.

trans-unit.source: An example of an extended right is [Send-As](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/adschema/adschema/r_send_as.asp), which gives a user the right to send e-mail for another user.
trans-unit.target: Et eksempel på en utvidet rettigheten [sende-som](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/adschema/adschema/r_send_as.asp), som gir en bruker rettighet til å sende e-post for en annen bruker.

trans-unit.source: For a list of possible extended rights, see the topic [Extended Rights](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/adschema/adschema/extended_rights.asp) in the MSDN Library at [http://msdn.microsoft.com/library](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library).
trans-unit.target: En liste over mulige utvidede rettigheter, kan du se emnet [utvidede rettighetene](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/adschema/adschema/extended_rights.asp) i MSDN-biblioteket på [http://msdn.microsoft.com/library](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library).

trans-unit.source: For more information about extended rights, see the topic [Control Access Rights](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/adschema/adschema/a_controlaccessrights.asp), also in the MSDN Library.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon om utvidede rettigheter, se emnet [kontrollen tilgangsrettigheter](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/adschema/adschema/a_controlaccessrights.asp), også i MSDN-biblioteket.
